Job Details
Required Graphic Designer Cum Video Editor with 2 to 5 years experience.
Requirements
Must have good knowledge and experience of working with Adobe InDesign, Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator, Adobe Premiere, Adobe AfterEffects, AutoCAD, Autodesk Maya, Autodesk 3DMax, Apple Final Cut Pro, Vray, Lightroom, etc. Must be good at English language. Arabic knowledge will be an advantage, but not compulsory. Must be able to work on Mac and PC. Knowledge of Photography and Videography preferred. Must be good at Fine Photo Retouching. Gulf experience preferred, but not compulsory.
